  _playerName: Have I not been of any help to you?
  _NPCName: LYBL
  _dialogueType: 0
  _startDialogue: 0
  linear:
    _pharases: []
    _responses: []
    _haveResponses: 0
  branching:
  - _Question:
    - ... you have.
    - ... no, you haven't.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Yipee! :)
    - . . .
    nextStepIndices: 010000000b000000
  - _Question:
    - But that doesn't mean I'm happy with you.
    _NpcResponses:
    - :(
    nextStepIndices: 02000000
  - _Question:
    - Don't give me that.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Sorry.
    nextStepIndices: 03000000
  - _Question:
    - We're gonna need to set boundaries.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Like what?
    nextStepIndices: 04000000
  - _Question:
    - Mainly? Don't do things without my explicit permission.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Sounds easy enough.
    nextStepIndices: 05000000
  - _Question:
    - And if you don't know how to do something I ask of you, you tell me.
    _NpcResponses:
    - But I know everything!
    nextStepIndices: 06000000
  - _Question:
    - That's debatable.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Okay, maybe not Latin...
    nextStepIndices: 07000000
  - _Question:
    - Or what not to email someone's boss.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Or what not to email someone's boss.
    nextStepIndices: 08000000
  - _Question:
    - Or what my girlfriend looks like.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Okay maybe I don't know as much as I think I do.
    nextStepIndices: 09000000
  - _Question:
    - So, do you agree to maintain those boundaries?
    _NpcResponses:
    - . . . I agree.
    nextStepIndices: 0a000000
  - _Question:
    - Good night, Lybl.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Good night!
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - You really do think that, huh.
    nextStepIndices: 0c000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - ... can I help you one last time?
    nextStepIndices: 0d000000
  - _Question:
    - What do you plan to do?
    _NpcResponses:
    - Well, my presence has clearly made your life worse.
    nextStepIndices: 0e000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - So I plan to... complete your last task.
    nextStepIndices: 0f000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - I hope that, one day, you can live your best life.
    nextStepIndices: 10000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Goodbye.
    nextStepIndices: 11000000
  - _Question:
    - Goodbye, Lybl.
    _NpcResponses:
    - 
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
